Nnwekọrịta nchekwa / faịlụ - a bụ nchekwa / faịlụ na-anaghị achọ onye ọrụ Nyocha *, na pụtara na ha dị maka niile ọbịa * (ma ọ bụrụ na ha nwere a njikọ). All ọrụ nwere ike ịmepụta dị otú ahụ nchekwa / faịlụ site na menu "Share → Mepụta a ọha njikọ". Otú ọ dị, na-akọrọ nchekwa nwere ike ịnwe mmachi ikikere: n'ihi na-ebugote, nbudata, faịlụ / nchekwa ndepụta. N'okpuru ebe a bụ table nke njikọ na-akọrọ nchekwa / faịlụ kere ọrụ. Na-arụ ọrụ ọha na njikọ Njirimara n'ụzọ ziri ezi ijide n'aka na-ahụ maka \ Anonymousdownload.ashx-enye ohere amaonye ohere IIS. Ị nwere ike ịlele a na nchọpụta nsogbu page.
